<style>
  .membership-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .membership-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -50%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,193,7,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .plan-card {
    border: none;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .plan-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15) !important;
  }
  .plan-card.featured {
    border: 2px solid #ffc107;
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }
  .plan-card.featured:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02) translateY(-8px);
  }
  .plan-card .popular-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #ff9800 100%);
    color: #000;
    padding: 0.35rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border-radius: 0 1.25rem 0 1rem;
  }
  .plan-card .plan-header {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .plan-card .plan-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .plan-card .plan-name {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .plan-card .plan-price {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #fff 100%);
  }
  .plan-card .price-main {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .plan-card .price-period {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #6c757d;
  }
  .plan-card .plan-features {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
  }
  .plan-card .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .plan-card .feature-icon {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .plan-card .plan-cta {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .plan-card .btn-subscribe {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .plan-card .btn-subscribe:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  .benefit-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .benefit-icon {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }
  .current-plan-badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .price-toggle {
    background: #f1f3f5;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 0.25rem;
    display: inline-flex;
  }
  .price-toggle .btn {
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: none;
  }
  .price-toggle .btn.active {
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .stats-pill {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767.98px) {
    .plan-card .price-main { font-size: 2rem; }
    .plan-card .plan-header { padding: 1.25rem 1rem 0.75rem; }
    .plan-card .plan-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.25rem; }
    .membership-hero { border-radius: 1rem; }
  }
  
  /* Price Toggle Switch Styles */
  .price-toggle-wrapper {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
  }
  .price-label {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #6c757d;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }
  .price-label.active {
    color: #212529;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .price-switch {
    position: relative;
    width: 56px;
    height: 28px;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .price-switch input {
    opacity: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
  }
  .price-slider {
    position: absolute;
    cursor: pointer;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    transition: 0.4s;
    border-radius: 28px;
  }
  .price-slider:before {
    position: absolute;
    content: "";
    height: 22px;
    width: 22px;
    left: 3px;
    bottom: 3px;
    background-color: white;
    transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }
  .price-switch input:checked + .price-slider {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
  }
  .price-switch input:checked + .price-slider:before {
    transform: translateX(28px);
  }
  .price-display {
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .price-display.fade-out {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(-10px);
  }
  .price-display.fade-in {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.3s ease forwards;
  }
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  .other-prices {
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  /* Plans Carousel Styles */
  .plans-carousel-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    padding: 0 50px;
  }
  .plans-carousel {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -ms-overflow-style: none;
    padding: 1rem 0.5rem 2rem;
  }
  .plans-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }
  .plans-carousel .plan-card {
    flex: 0 0 300px;
    min-width: 280px;
    max-width: 320px;
  }
  .carousel-btn {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 10;
    color: #495057;
  }
  .carousel-btn:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: transparent;
    transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.1);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
  }
  .carousel-btn:active {
    transform: translateY(-50%) scale(0.95);
  }
  .carousel-btn.prev {
    left: 0;
  }
  .carousel-btn.next {
    right: 0;
  }
  .carousel-btn:disabled {
    opacity: 0.3;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
  .carousel-btn:disabled:hover {
    background: #fff;
    color: #495057;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .carousel-dots {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .carousel-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #dee2e6;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .carousel-dot.active {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    width: 28px;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }
  .carousel-dot:hover:not(.active) {
    background: #adb5bd;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767.98px) {
    .plans-carousel-wrapper {
      padding: 0 40px;
    }
    .carousel-btn {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
    }
    .plans-carousel .plan-card {
      flex: 0 0 260px;
      min-width: 260px;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 575.98px) {
    .plans-carousel-wrapper {
      padding: 0 35px;
    }
    .carousel-btn {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .plans-carousel .plan-card {
      flex: 0 0 85vw;
      min-width: 85vw;
      max-width: 85vw;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  function togglePricing() {
    const toggle = document.getElementById('pricingToggle');
    const isAnnual = toggle.checked;
    
    // Update labels
    document.querySelectorAll('.price-label').forEach(label => {
      label.classList.remove('active');
    });
    document.querySelector(`.price-label[data-period="${isAnnual ? 'annual' : 'monthly'}"]`).classList.add('active');
    
    // Animate price change
    document.querySelectorAll('.monthly-price').forEach(el => {
      if (isAnnual) {
        el.classList.add('fade-out');
        setTimeout(() => {
          el.style.display = 'none';
        }, 150);
      } else {
        el.style.display = 'block';
        el.classList.remove('fade-out');
        el.classList.add('fade-in');
        setTimeout(() => el.classList.remove('fade-in'), 300);
      }
    });
    
    document.querySelectorAll('.annual-price').forEach(el => {
      if (isAnnual) {
        setTimeout(() => {
          el.style.display = 'block';
          el.classList.add('fade-in');
          setTimeout(() => el.classList.remove('fade-in'), 300);
        }, 150);
      } else {
        el.classList.add('fade-out');
        setTimeout(() => {
          el.style.display = 'none';
          el.classList.remove('fade-out');
        }, 150);
      }
    });
    
    // Hide/show other prices
    document.querySelectorAll('.other-prices').forEach(el => {
      el.style.opacity = isAnnual ? '0' : '1';
    });
  }
  
  // Initialize on page load
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    document.querySelector('.price-label[data-period="annual"]').classList.add('active');
    document.getElementById('pricingToggle').checked = true;
    togglePricing();
    initCarousel();
  });
  
  // Carousel functionality
  function initCarousel() {
    const carousel = document.getElementById('plansCarousel');
    const prevBtn = document.getElementById('carouselPrev');
    const nextBtn = document.getElementById('carouselNext');
    const dotsContainer = document.getElementById('carouselDots');
    
    if (!carousel) return;
    
    const cards = carousel.querySelectorAll('.plan-card');
    const cardWidth = cards[0]?.offsetWidth + 20 || 320; // card width + gap
    let currentIndex = 0;
    
    // Create dots
    cards.forEach((_, index) => {
      const dot = document.createElement('button');
      dot.className = `carousel-dot ${index === 0 ? 'active' : ''}`;
      dot.onclick = () => scrollToCard(index);
      dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);
    });
    
    function updateDots() {
      const scrollLeft = carousel.scrollLeft;
      const newIndex = Math.round(scrollLeft / cardWidth);
      currentIndex = Math.min(Math.max(newIndex, 0), cards.length - 1);
      
      document.querySelectorAll('.carousel-dot').forEach((dot, i) => {
        dot.classList.toggle('active', i === currentIndex);
      });
      
      // Update button states
      prevBtn.disabled = currentIndex === 0;
      nextBtn.disabled = currentIndex >= cards.length - 1;
    }
    
    function scrollToCard(index) {
      currentIndex = index;
      carousel.scrollTo({
        left: index * cardWidth,
        behavior: 'smooth'
      });
      setTimeout(updateDots, 300);
    }
    
    prevBtn.onclick = () => {
      if (currentIndex > 0) {
        scrollToCard(currentIndex - 1);
      }
    };
    
    nextBtn.onclick = () => {
      if (currentIndex < cards.length - 1) {
        scrollToCard(currentIndex + 1);
      }
    };
    
    // Update dots on scroll
    carousel.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      clearTimeout(carousel.scrollTimeout);
      carousel.scrollTimeout = setTimeout(updateDots, 100);
    });
    
    // Initial state
    updateDots();
    
    // Touch/swipe support is native with overflow-x: auto
  }
</script>

<div class="container-fluid px-3 px-md-4 py-4">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="membership-hero text-white p-4 p-md-5 mb-4">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <%= link_to turista_dashboard_index_path, class: "btn btn-sm btn-outline-light rounded-pill" do %>
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-1"></i> Volver
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <h1 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);">
          <i class="fas fa-crown text-warning me-2"></i>
          Membresías Iyai Club
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-4 opacity-75" style="max-width: 500px;">
          Desbloquea descuentos exclusivos, acumula más puntos y disfruta de beneficios únicos en cada viaje.
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div class="stats-pill">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            <span><strong>+2,500</strong> miembros activos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stats-pill">
            <i class="fas fa-building"></i>
            <span><strong>+150</strong> establecimientos</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 mt-4 mt-lg-0">
        <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-4 p-4 backdrop-blur">
          <div class="text-center mb-3">
            <% if @active_membership %>
              <% if @active_membership.in_grace_period? %>
                <div class="current-plan-badge mb-2" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #fd7e14 100%); color: #212529;">
                  <i class="fas fa-hourglass-half"></i> En Prórroga
                </div>
              <% elsif @active_membership.pending_cancellation? %>
                <div class="current-plan-badge mb-2" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c757d 0%, #495057 100%);">
                  <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Cancelación pendiente
                </div>
              <% else %>
                <div class="current-plan-badge mb-2">
                  <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Plan Activo
                </div>
              <% end %>
              <h4 class="fw-bold mb-1"><%= PlanPrice.find_by(id: @active_membership.plan_type)&.plan&.name || "Membresía" %></h4>
              <% if @active_membership.in_grace_period? %>
                <small style="color: #ffc107;">Prórroga hasta: <%= @active_membership.grace_period_until.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></small>
              <% elsif @active_membership.pending_cancellation? %>
                <small class="opacity-75">Activa hasta: <%= @active_membership.end_date&.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></small>
              <% else %>
                <small class="opacity-75">Vence: <%= @active_membership.end_date&.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></small>
              <% end %>
            <% else %>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <i class="fas fa-user-circle fa-3x opacity-50"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1">Sin membresía activa</h5>
              <small class="opacity-75">¡Elige un plan y comienza a ahorrar!</small>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <hr class="border-light opacity-25">
          <div class="small">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-2">
              <span class="opacity-75"><i class="fas fa-tag me-2"></i>Tu descuento</span>
              <strong><%= current_user.discount_percentage %>%</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-2">
              <span class="opacity-75"><i class="fas fa-coins me-2"></i>Ratio puntos</span>
              <strong><%= current_user.points_ratio[:points] %> pts / $<%= current_user.points_ratio[:per_dollars] %></strong>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
              <span class="opacity-75"><i class="fas fa-star me-2"></i>Tus puntos</span>
              <strong><%= number_with_delimiter(current_user.total_points) %></strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Panel de gestión de membresía activa -->
  <% if @active_membership %>
    <div class="mb-4">

      <%# Alerta: prórroga activa por impago %>
      <% if @active_membership.in_grace_period? %>
        <div class="alert alert-warning border-0 rounded-3 shadow-sm d-flex gap-3 align-items-start" role="alert">
          <div class="fs-4 mt-1">⏳</div>
          <div>
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Prórroga activa por renovación pendiente</h6>
            <p class="mb-2 small">
              Tu membresía venció pero hemos activado una prórroga de 5 días. Sigues teniendo acceso a todos
              tus beneficios hasta el <strong><%= @active_membership.grace_period_until.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></strong>.
              Renueva antes de esa fecha para no perderlos.
            </p>
            <%= link_to "#planes", class: "btn btn-warning btn-sm fw-semibold" do %>
              <i class="fas fa-sync-alt me-1"></i> Renovar mi membresía
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>

      <%# Alerta: vence pronto (7 días) %>
      <% elsif @active_membership.expiring_soon?(7) && !@active_membership.pending_cancellation? %>
        <div class="alert alert-info border-0 rounded-3 shadow-sm d-flex gap-3 align-items-start" role="alert">
          <div class="fs-4 mt-1">📅</div>
          <div>
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Tu membresía vence pronto</h6>
            <p class="mb-2 small">
              Tu plan <strong><%= @active_membership.plan_name %></strong> vence el
              <strong><%= @active_membership.end_date.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></strong>.
              Renueva para no interrumpir tus beneficios.
            </p>
            <%= link_to "#planes", class: "btn btn-info btn-sm fw-semibold text-white" do %>
              <i class="fas fa-sync-alt me-1"></i> Renovar ahora
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>

      <%# Alerta: cancelación voluntaria pendiente %>
      <% elsif @active_membership.pending_cancellation? %>
        <div class="alert alert-secondary border-0 rounded-3 shadow-sm d-flex gap-3 align-items-start" role="alert">
          <div class="fs-4 mt-1">🔔</div>
          <div class="flex-grow-1">
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Cancelación programada</h6>
            <p class="mb-2 small">
              Has cancelado tu membresía. Seguirás disfrutando de todos los beneficios del plan
              <strong><%= @active_membership.plan_name %></strong> hasta el
              <strong><%= @active_membership.end_date.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></strong>.
              ¿Cambiaste de opinión?
            </p>
            <%= button_to reactivate_turista_membership_path(@active_membership),
                method: :patch,
                class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm fw-semibold",
                data: { confirm: "¿Quieres reactivar tu membresía?" } do %>
              <i class="fas fa-undo me-1"></i> Deshacer cancelación
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <!-- Tarjeta de gestión de membresía -->
      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-3">
        <div class="card-header bg-white border-bottom py-3 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
          <h5 class="fw-bold mb-0">
            <i class="fas fa-id-card text-primary me-2"></i>
            Gestión de membresía
          </h5>
          <% days_left = (@active_membership.end_date - Date.current).to_i rescue 0 %>
          <% if @active_membership.in_grace_period? %>
            <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">
              <i class="fas fa-hourglass-half me-1"></i>
              Prórroga: <%= ((@active_membership.grace_period_until - Date.current).to_i rescue 0) %> días
            </span>
          <% elsif days_left > 0 %>
            <span class="badge bg-success">
              <i class="fas fa-clock me-1"></i>
              <%= days_left %> <%= days_left == 1 ? "día restante" : "días restantes" %>
            </span>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="row g-3 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex gap-3 align-items-center">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary"
                     style="width: 56px; height: 56px; font-size: 1.4rem;">
                  <i class="fas fa-crown"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-bold fs-6"><%= @active_membership.plan_name %></div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">
                    Vigente desde <%= @active_membership.start_date&.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="small">
                    <% if @active_membership.in_grace_period? %>
                      <span class="text-warning fw-semibold">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-1"></i>
                        Prórroga hasta <%= @active_membership.grace_period_until.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %>
                      </span>
                    <% elsif @active_membership.pending_cancellation? %>
                      <span class="text-muted">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock me-1"></i>
                        Activa hasta <%= @active_membership.end_date&.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %>
                      </span>
                    <% else %>
                      <span class="text-success">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-check me-1"></i>
                        Vence el <%= @active_membership.end_date&.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %>
                      </span>
                    <% end %>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-content-md-end">
                <%# Botón cambiar plan: lleva a la sección de planes en la misma página %>
                <% unless @active_membership.pending_cancellation? || @active_membership.in_grace_period? %>
                  <%= link_to "#planes", class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm fw-semibold" do %>
                    <i class="fas fa-exchange-alt me-1"></i> Cambiar plan
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>

                <%# Botón cancelar membresía (solo si no está ya cancelada ni en prórroga) %>
                <% unless @active_membership.pending_cancellation? || @active_membership.in_grace_period? %>
                  <%= button_to cancel_turista_membership_path(@active_membership),
                      method: :patch,
                      class: "btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm fw-semibold",
                      data: {
                        confirm: "¿Seguro que deseas cancelar tu membresía? Seguirás teniendo acceso hasta el #{@active_membership.end_date&.strftime('%d/%m/%Y')}."
                      } do %>
                    <i class="fas fa-times-circle me-1"></i> Cancelar membresía
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>

                <%# Deshacer cancelación %>
                <% if @active_membership.pending_cancellation? %>
                  <%= button_to reactivate_turista_membership_path(@active_membership),
                      method: :patch,
                      class: "btn btn-success btn-sm fw-semibold",
                      data: { confirm: "¿Quieres reactivar tu membresía?" } do %>
                    <i class="fas fa-undo me-1"></i> Reactivar membresía
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%# Info adicional: qué pasa al cancelar %>
          <% unless @active_membership.pending_cancellation? || @active_membership.in_grace_period? %>
            <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-top">
              <small class="text-muted">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-1 text-info"></i>
                Si cancelas, seguirás teniendo todos los beneficios hasta que venza tu período actual el
                <strong><%= @active_membership.end_date&.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></strong>.
                No se realizan reembolsos proporcionales.
              </small>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <!-- Plans Section -->
  <div class="mb-5" id="planes">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">Elige tu Plan Ideal</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">Todos los planes incluyen acceso completo a la plataforma</p>
      
      <!-- Price Toggle Switch -->
      <div class="price-toggle-wrapper d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-3 bg-light rounded-pill p-2 shadow-sm">
        <span class="price-label" data-period="monthly">Mensual</span>
        <label class="price-switch">
          <input type="checkbox" id="pricingToggle" onchange="togglePricing()" checked>
          <span class="price-slider"></span>
        </label>
        <span class="price-label" data-period="annual">
          Anual
          <span class="badge bg-success ms-1" style="font-size: 0.65rem;">-25%</span>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if @available_plans.any? %>
      <% plan_colors = { 
        'free' => { bg: '#e9ecef', icon: '#6c757d', btn: 'secondary' },
        'basico' => { bg: '#e3f2fd', icon: '#1976d2', btn: 'primary' },
        'bronce' => { bg: '#fff3e0', icon: '#e65100', btn: 'warning' },
        'gold' => { bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9c4 0%, #ffecb3 100%)', icon: '#ffc107', btn: 'warning' },
        'platinum' => { bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #e8eaf6 0%, #c5cae9 100%)', icon: '#5c6bc0', btn: 'dark' },
        'gold_estudiantil' => { bg: '#e8f5e9', icon: '#43a047', btn: 'success' }
      } %>
      
      <div class="plans-carousel-wrapper">
        <!-- Previous Button -->
        <button class="carousel-btn prev" id="carouselPrev" aria-label="Plan anterior">
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
        </button>
        
        <!-- Carousel Container -->
        <div class="plans-carousel" id="plansCarousel">
          <% grouped_plans = @available_plans.group_by { |pp| pp.plan&.name || pp.plan_type }
             sorted_plans = grouped_plans.sort_by do |_plan_name, prices|
               plan = prices.first.plan
               plan_key = plan&.plan_key || 'basico'
               plan_key == 'gold_estudiantil' ? 0 : 1
             end %>
          <% sorted_plans.each_with_index do |(plan_name, prices), index| %>
            <% plan = prices.first.plan %>
            <% plan_key = plan&.plan_key || 'basico' %>
            <% colors = plan_colors[plan_key] || plan_colors['basico'] %>
            <% is_featured = plan_key == 'gold' %>
            <% is_active = @active_membership && prices.any? { |p| p.id.to_s == @active_membership.plan_type.to_s } %>
            <% monthly_price = prices.find { |p| p.duration == 1 } %>
            <% annual_price = prices.find { |p| p.duration == 12 } %>
            <% annual_monthly_equivalent = annual_price ? (annual_price.price.to_f / 12) : nil %>
            <div class="plan-card shadow-sm h-100 <%= 'featured' if is_featured %> <%= 'border border-success border-2' if is_active %>">
              <% if is_featured %>
                <div class="popular-badge">
                  <i class="fas fa-fire me-1"></i> Más Popular
                </div>
              <% end %>
              
              <div class="plan-header">
                <div class="plan-icon" style="background: <%= colors[:bg] %>; color: <%= colors[:icon] %>;">
                  <% case plan_key %>
                  <% when 'free' %>
                    <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                  <% when 'basico' %>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <% when 'bronce' %>
                    <i class="fas fa-medal"></i>
                  <% when 'gold', 'gold_estudiantil' %>
                    <i class="fas fa-crown"></i>
                  <% when 'platinum' %>
                    <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
                  <% else %>
                    <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
                <h3 class="plan-name"><%= plan_name %></h3>
                <% if plan&.is_student_plan %>
                  <span class="badge bg-success bg-opacity-10 text-success">
                    <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap me-1"></i> Estudiantes
                  </span>
                <% end %>
                <% if is_active %>
                  <div class="mt-2">
                    <span class="badge bg-success">
                      <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-1"></i> Tu plan actual
                    </span>
                  </div>
                <% end %>
              </div>

              <div class="plan-price text-center">
                <% if monthly_price %>
                  <!-- Monthly Price -->
                  <div class="price-display monthly-price">
                    <div class="price-main" style="color: <%= colors[:icon] %>;">
                      $<%= number_with_precision(monthly_price.price, precision: 0) %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="price-period">/mes</div>
                  </div>
                  <!-- Annual Price (shown as monthly equivalent with discount) -->
                  <% if annual_price %>
                    <div class="price-display annual-price" style="display: none;">
                      <div class="price-main" style="color: <%= colors[:icon] %>;">
                        $<%= number_with_precision(annual_monthly_equivalent, precision: 2) %>
                      </div>
                      <div class="price-period">/mes</div>
                      <div class="mt-1">
                        <small class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">
                          Facturado anualmente ($<%= number_with_precision(annual_price.price, precision: 0) %>)
                        </small>
                      </div>
                      <div class="mt-2">
                        <span class="badge bg-success small">
                          <i class="fas fa-piggy-bank me-1"></i>
                          Ahorras $<%= number_with_precision((monthly_price.price * 12) - annual_price.price, precision: 0) %> al año
                        </span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                  <!-- 6 months price indicator -->
                  <% six_month_price = prices.find { |p| p.duration == 6 } %>
                  <% if six_month_price %>
                    <div class="mt-2 other-prices">
                      <small class="text-muted">
                        6 meses: <strong>$<%= number_with_precision(six_month_price.price, precision: 0) %></strong>
                      </small>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                <% else %>
                  <div class="price-display">
                    <div class="price-main text-success">Gratis</div>
                    <div class="price-period">Para siempre</div>
                  </div>
                <% end %>
              </div>

              <div class="plan-features">
                <% if plan %>
                  <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon bg-success bg-opacity-10 text-success">
                      <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span>
                      <strong><%= plan.discount_percentage || 0 %>%</strong> descuento en hospedaje
                      <% if plan.fixed_discount.to_i > 0 %>
                        <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark ms-1" style="font-size: 0.65rem;">+<%= plan.fixed_discount %>% fijo</span>
                      <% end %>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon bg-warning bg-opacity-10 text-warning">
                      <i class="fas fa-coins"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span><strong><%= plan.points_earned || 1 %></strong> puntos por cada $<%= plan.dollars_per_point || 5 %></span>
                  </div>

                  <% if plan.pool_visits_per_year.to_i > 0 %>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                      <div class="feature-icon bg-info bg-opacity-10 text-info">
                        <i class="fas fa-swimming-pool"></i>
                      </div>
                      <span>
                        <strong><%= plan.pool_visits_per_year %></strong> visitas piscina/año
                        <% if plan.max_pool_guests.to_i > 0 %>
                          <span class="text-muted d-block" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-friends me-1"></i>
                            Hasta <strong><%= plan.max_pool_guests %></strong> <%= plan.max_pool_guests == 1 ? 'persona' : 'personas' %>
                          </span>
                        <% end %>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>

                  <% if plan.free_nights.to_i > 0 %>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                      <div class="feature-icon bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-bed"></i>
                      </div>
                      <span>
                        <strong><%= plan.free_nights %></strong> noches + <strong><%= plan.free_days %></strong> días gratis
                        <% if plan.includes_breakfast %>
                          <i class="fas fa-coffee text-warning ms-1" title="Incluye desayuno"></i>
                        <% end %>
                        <% if plan.includes_dinner %>
                          <i class="fas fa-utensils text-warning ms-1" title="Incluye cena"></i>
                        <% end %>
                        <% if plan.max_lodging_guests.to_i > 0 %>
                          <span class="text-muted d-block" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-friends me-1"></i>
                            Hasta <strong><%= plan.max_lodging_guests %></strong> <%= plan.max_lodging_guests == 1 ? 'persona' : 'personas' %>
                          </span>
                        <% end %>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>

                  <% if plan.events_access %>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                      <div class="feature-icon bg-success bg-opacity-10 text-success">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
                      </div>
                      <span>Eventos <strong>gratis</strong></span>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
              </div>

              <div class="plan-cta">
                <% if is_active %>
                  <button class="btn btn-success btn-subscribe w-100" disabled>
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i> Plan Activo
                  </button>
                <% elsif plan_key == 'free' %>
                  <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-subscribe w-100" disabled>
                    Plan Actual
                  </button>
                <% else %>
                  <%= link_to new_subscription_path(plan_id: (annual_price || monthly_price)&.id), 
                      class: "btn btn-#{colors[:btn]} btn-subscribe w-100" do %>
                    <i class="fas fa-rocket me-2"></i> Comenzar Ahora
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Next Button -->
        <button class="carousel-btn next" id="carouselNext" aria-label="Siguiente plan">
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Carousel Dots -->
      <div class="carousel-dots" id="carouselDots"></div>
    <% else %>
      <div class="text-center py-5">
        <i class="fas fa-crown fa-4x text-muted mb-3"></i>
        <h5 class="text-muted">No hay planes disponibles actualmente</h5>
        <p class="text-muted">Pronto tendremos nuevos planes para ti</p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">¿Por qué ser miembro?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">Beneficios exclusivos que transformarán tus viajes</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row g-3 g-md-4">
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="benefit-card h-100">
          <div class="benefit-icon bg-success bg-opacity-10 text-success">
            <i class="fas fa-percentage"></i>
          </div>
          <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">Descuentos</h6>
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Hasta 50% en hospedajes</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="benefit-card h-100">
          <div class="benefit-icon bg-warning bg-opacity-10 text-warning">
            <i class="fas fa-coins"></i>
          </div>
          <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">Puntos</h6>
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Acumula y canjea</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="benefit-card h-100">
          <div class="benefit-icon bg-info bg-opacity-10 text-info">
            <i class="fas fa-swimming-pool"></i>
          </div>
          <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">Piscinas</h6>
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Acceso gratuito</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="benefit-card h-100">
          <div class="benefit-icon bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary">
            <i class="fas fa-bed"></i>
          </div>
          <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">Noches</h6>
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Hospedaje gratis</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="benefit-card h-100">
          <div class="benefit-icon bg-danger bg-opacity-10 text-danger">
            <i class="fas fa-calendar-star"></i>
          </div>
          <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">Eventos</h6>
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Entrada gratuita</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="benefit-card h-100">
          <div class="benefit-icon bg-secondary bg-opacity-10 text-secondary">
            <i class="fas fa-headset"></i>
          </div>
          <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">Soporte</h6>
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">WhatsApp 24/7</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4">
    <div class="card-body p-4">
      <h5 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-question-circle me-2 text-info"></i>
        Preguntas Frecuentes
      </h5>
      <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-item border-0">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
              ¿Cómo funcionan los descuentos?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body text-muted small">
              Los descuentos se aplican automáticamente al momento de realizar tu reserva en cualquiera de nuestros establecimientos afiliados. El porcentaje varía según tu plan y la temporada.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item border-0">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
              ¿Puedo cambiar de plan en cualquier momento?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body text-muted small">
              Sí, puedes actualizar tu plan en cualquier momento. El cambio se aplicará inmediatamente y se ajustará el cobro de forma proporcional.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item border-0">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
              ¿Cómo canjeo mis noches gratis?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body text-muted small">
              Contacta a nuestro equipo de soporte por WhatsApp para coordinar tu estadía gratuita. Las noches están sujetas a disponibilidad y aplican términos y condiciones.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
